<p><div align="center"><table width="50%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
<td width="150"><br></td>
<td align="center"><b>
<i>Perdita cephalotes</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Cresson, 1878&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Macrotera cephalotes </i>Cresson, 1878; <i>Perdita &#40;Procockerellia&#41; excellens </i>Timberlake, 1958; <i>Perdita &#40;Cockerellia&#41; autumnalis </i>Timberlake, 1977</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Andrenidae">Andrenidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Perdita">Perdita</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Xeromacrotera&name=Perdita&flags=subgenus:"><i>Xeromacrotera</i></a></small>
</td></tr></table><p>
<p>
<table width="80%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td>
<div align="center">
<table><tr><td valign="top" align="center"><a href="/mp/20m?kind=Perdita+cephalotes"><img src="/nh/maps/Insecta/Hymenoptera/Apoidea/Andrenidae/Perdita/map_of_Perdita_cephalotes.jpg" width="360" height="180" border="0"></a><br><font color="red" size="-1" face="sans-serif">Click on map for details about points.</font>
<p><div align="center"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="50%"><tr><td nowrap><b>IDnature guide</b></td></tr><tr><td nowrap><ul><li><a href="/mp/20q?guide=Apoidea_species&flags=HAS:" target="_top">
Bee species</a></li>
</ul></td></tr></table></div>
</td></tr></table></div><p>
